text.div:
Claim Medicare Non Payment Reason Code

The reason that no Medicare payment is made for services on an institutional claim. Source: https://bluebutton.cms.gov/resources/variables/clmmdcrnonpmtrsn_cd

This code system https://bluebutton.cms.gov/assets/ig/CodeSystem-clm-mdcr-non-pmt-rsn-cd defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
A Covered worker's compensation (Obsolete)Covered worker's compensation (Obsolete)
B Benefit exhaustedBenefit exhausted
C Custodial care – non-covered care (includes all 'beneficiary at fault' waiver cases) (Obsolete)Custodial care – non-covered care (includes all 'beneficiary at fault' waiver cases) (Obsolete)
E HMO out-of-plan services not emergency or urgently needed (Obsolete)HMO out-of-plan services not emergency or urgently needed (Obsolete)
E MSP cost avoided - IRS/SSA/HCFA Data Match (eff. 7/00)MSP cost avoided - IRS/SSA/HCFA Data Match (eff. 7/00)
F MSP cost avoid HMO Rate Cell (eff. 7/00)MSP cost avoid HMO Rate Cell (eff. 7/00)
G MSP cost avoided Litigation Settlement (eff. 7/00)MSP cost avoided Litigation Settlement (eff. 7/00)
H MSP cost avoided Employer Voluntary Reporting (eff. 7/00)MSP cost avoided Employer Voluntary Reporting (eff. 7/00)
J MSP cost avoid Insurer Voluntary Reporting (eff. 7/00)MSP cost avoid Insurer Voluntary Reporting (eff. 7/00)
K MSP cost avoid Initial Enrollment Questionnaire (eff. 7/00)MSP cost avoid Initial Enrollment Questionnaire (eff. 7/00)
N All other reasons for non-paymentAll other reasons for non-payment
P Payment requestedPayment requested
Q MSP cost avoided Voluntary Agreement (eff. 7/00)MSP cost avoided Voluntary Agreement (eff. 7/00)
R Benefits refused, or evidence not submittedBenefits refused, or evidence not submitted
T MSP cost avoided - IEQ contractor (eff. 9/76) (obsolete 6/30/00)MSP cost avoided - IEQ contractor (eff. 9/76) (obsolete 6/30/00)
U MSP cost avoided - HMO rate cell adjustment (eff. 9/76) (Obsolete 6/30/00)MSP cost avoided - HMO rate cell adjustment (eff. 9/76) (Obsolete 6/30/00)
V MSP cost avoided - litigation settlement (eff. 9/76) (Obsolete 6/30/00)MSP cost avoided - litigation settlement (eff. 9/76) (Obsolete 6/30/00)
W Worker's compensation (Obsolete)Worker's compensation (Obsolete)
X MSP cost avoided - genericMSP cost avoided - generic
Y MSP cost avoided - IRS/SSA data match project (obsolete 6/30/00)MSP cost avoided - IRS/SSA data match project (obsolete 6/30/00)
Z Zero reimbursement RAPs -- zero reimbursement made due to medical review intervention or where provider specific zero payment has been determined. (effective with HHPPS - 10/00)Zero reimbursement RAPs -- zero reimbursement made due to medical review intervention or where provider specific zero payment has been determined. (effective with HHPPS - 10/00)
00 MSP cost avoided - COB ContractorMSP cost avoided - COB Contractor

13 MSP cost avoided - Office of Personnel ManagementMSP cost avoided - Office of Personnel Management

16 MSP cost avoided - Liability Insurer VDSA (eff. 4/2006)MSP cost avoided - Liability Insurer VDSA (eff. 4/2006)
17 MSP cost avoided - No-Fault Insurer VDSA (eff. 4/2006)MSP cost avoided - No-Fault Insurer VDSA (eff. 4/2006)
18 MSP cost avoided - Pharmacy Benefit Manager Data Sharing Agreement (eff. 4/2006)MSP cost avoided - Pharmacy Benefit Manager Data Sharing Agreement (eff. 4/2006)
19 SEE NOTE4: Coordination of Benefits Contractor 11119 (see CMS Change Request 7906 for identification of the contractor.)SEE NOTE4: Coordination of Benefits Contractor 11119 (see CMS Change Request 7906 for identification of the contractor.)

25 MSP cost avoided - Recovery Audit Contractor - California (eff. 10/2005)MSP cost avoided - Recovery Audit Contractor - California (eff. 10/2005)

Effective 4/1/02, the Medicare nonpayment reason code was expanded to a 2-byte field. The NCH instituted a crosswalk from the 2-byte code to a 1-byte character code. Below are the character codes (found in NCH & NMUD).
